      <h3 class="heading-31">Sales. Service. Supplies.</h3>
      <p class="paragraph-32">Thank you for visiting our site. We are dedicated to helping you find the perfect Point of Sales system or equipment you need to run your business. We offer state of the art terminals, electronic cash registers, kitchen display equipment, CAS Scales, video surveillance equipment, printers and supplies. In addition to sales, we also service your equipment.</p>
